title: BRIGHT AND LIGHT UNIT IN PARAMOUNT WORLD!!
posting_body: ['Bright and light 1 BD + DEN apartment with 2 FULL baths, and vast balcony.', 'Private elevator with only your hall, spacious den (with a bunk-bed) and the closet.', 'Huge walk in closet in the master bedroom with king-size bed.', 'Unit goes with 1 assigned parking spot + valet.', 'Stunning amenities in Paramount building - several pools (with skydeck pool), lounge areas, spa, fitness with boxing area, yoga studio, tennis courts, soccer field, cinema room, game room, children area, summer kitchen with BBQ, bar, even food market in the building and many more.', 'Convenient location - walking distance to Bayfront Park, FTX Arena, Perez Art Museum and park and cafes, 2 mins to metromover.', 'Close to NIU restaurant, Novikov, Zuma etc.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
